      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_044_000181",
    "sentence": "徐來兄至衡山，太子與飲，以刃刑傷之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_044_000182",
    "sentence": "后以此怨太子，數惡之於王。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_044_000183",
    "sentence": "女弟無采嫁，棄歸，與客姦。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_044_000184",
    "sentence": "太子數以數讓之，無采怒，不與太子通。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 0,
